<subSubSection pageId="5" pageNumber="480" type="description">
<paragraph blockId="5.[151,1436,943,1184]" pageId="5" pageNumber="480">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,1027,980,1005]" pageId="5" pageNumber="480">Recorded damage and economic importance in the orchards of Iran:</emphasis>
Mild and unknown. Recorded from leaves and branches of grapevine, fig and walnut (
<bibRefCitation box="[712,925,1015,1040]" pageId="5" pageNumber="480" refId="ref19127" refString="Farahbakhsh, Gh. (1961) A checklist of economically important insects and other enemies of plants and agricultural products in Iran. Plant organization Press, Tehran, 153 pp." type="book">Farahbakhsh 1961</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="5.[151,1436,943,1184]" box="[199,1096,1052,1077]" pageId="5" pageNumber="480">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,934,1052,1077]" pageId="5" pageNumber="480">Recorded damage in the orchards of other parts of the world:</emphasis>
Not recorded.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="5.[151,1436,943,1184]" pageId="5" pageNumber="480">
<materialsCitation ID-GBIF-Occurrence="1915496050" country="Iran" location="Alborz" pageId="5" pageNumber="480" specimenCount="1" stateProvince="Alborz">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[245,610,1087,1112]" pageId="5" pageNumber="480">
Recorded distribution in 
<collectingCountry box="[548,605,1087,1112]" name="Iran" pageId="5" pageNumber="480">Iran</collectingCountry>
:
</emphasis>
North, northwest, southern slopes of 
<collectingRegion box="[1036,1114,1087,1112]" country="Iran" name="Alborz" pageId="5" pageNumber="480">Alborz</collectingRegion>
and southwest (
<bibRefCitation pageId="5" pageNumber="480" refId="ref20738" refString="Mozaffarian, F. &amp; Wilson, M. R. (2011) An annotated checklist of the planthoppers of Iran (Hemiptera, Auchenorrhyncha, Fulgoromorpha) with distribution data. Zookeys, 145, 1 - 57. https: // doi. org / 10.3897 / zookeys. 145.1846" type="journal article">Mozaffarian &amp; Wilson 2011</bibRefCitation>
).
</materialsCitation>
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="5.[151,1436,943,1184]" box="[199,854,1159,1184]" pageId="5" pageNumber="480">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,342,1159,1184]" pageId="5" pageNumber="480">Conclusion:</emphasis>
Pest status of the species needs to be studied.
</paragraph>
